      <head>Louis Schiff</head>
      <div>

        <p>Possibly the brother of <ref cRef="entity-000782">Paul</ref> and <ref
            cRef="entity-000783">Viktor</ref> Schiff, thus brother of <ref cRef="entity-000771"
            >Jeanette Schenker</ref>.</p>

        <p>Only one reference to Louis has come to light so far in Schenker's diary: "Lie-Liechen
          finds two letters from Paul, from which a stay with brother Louis could be deduced."
          (September 13, 1919). Thus the identification is tentative. â€” It is known that Jeanette
          had five sisters and three brothers.</p>
